msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "You know, there's been a drone\r\nflying 'round here the past few days."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "For real? I've never actually seen one!\r\nIsn't flying them here illegal, though?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "No clue."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "A drone...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "What in the...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, you two?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Well, uh... We almost got hit by a drone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "A drone?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Huh? You don't know about them?\r\nThey're like little remote-control helicopters."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "That technology is news to me...\r\nMore importantly, one attacked you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "I don't know if it was aiming for us,\r\nbut was definitely flying in our direction."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "We dodged it though, and it just flew off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "And do you remember where it was heading?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Hm? Ummm, probably that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "What the!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "So that's a drone, huh?\r\nWhat is it doing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "It went that way.\r\nI should get after it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Not again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Hm? It's not flying away?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Maybe it wants to play a game of tag.\r\nGet back here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "You done playing now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "P-Please help me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Th-Thank god! You're finally here!\r\nPlease, you have to help me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Slow down. What's wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I can explain it all to you later.\r\nRight now we need to go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Hey there, pretty boy.\r\nWhere're you runnin' off to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Crap..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Who are you guys?\r\nWhat's your beef with this kid?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Ah, we don't got a beef at all.\r\nWe're just some friends lookin' to hang."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "H-He's lying!\r\nThese guys are blackmailing me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "They make me use that drone to record the city!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "C'mon, you're gonna give him the wrong idea!\r\nQuit your fakin', punk!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Nobody could fake the fear in his eyes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "I'm tellin' you, just get lost already!\r\nYou ain't lookin' to get pummeled, are ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "You can't just prey on an innocent kid like this.\r\nThat's not what yakuza do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Thanks for the lesson.\r\nI'm thinkin' we should return the favor..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "...by breakin' your legs!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whoa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "It's time for an explanation.\r\nTell me what happened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "W-Well, I was flying my drone at a park\r\nin Kamurocho about six months ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "But then the drone started acting weird,\r\nand then... totally stopped working."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "It fell right on top of these guys.\r\nI didn't realize they were yakuza..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Sounds like you were at fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Y-Yes, I agree!\r\nI apologized to them nonstop afterward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "I even said my parents would\r\ncover their hospital bills, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "...they weren't interested in that.\r\nThey had their own idea of payback."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Since then, I've been locked up here.\r\nDay in and day out, I fly that drone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "I don't understand.\r\nWhy would they want you to do that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "I'm pretty sure they were looking\r\nfor info on the city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "The more I flew, the more I realized\r\npeople don't expect surveillance from above."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "They'll do all sorts of stuff they don't want\r\nothers seeing. But I could see it all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Right, information is money.\r\nThat's a lesson you learn early in this city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "But... I wanted to get away.\r\nI'd always fly low when I got the chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "I was hoping someone'd chase after the drone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "But people just got scared instead.\r\nNobody ever came to help me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "But when I saw you, it seemed\r\nlike the perfect chance to try again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "You seemed strong, so I thought\r\nyou'd be able to save me if I got you here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "So that business with the drone was just an SOS?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "You could have really hurt someone, you know.\r\nBe more careful next time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "I will. Sorry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Now get going.\r\nYour family must be worried."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "R-Right. Um, thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "They really used this for surveillance?\r\nI can't believe the technology nowadays..."
msgstr ""

